    cc.owner_id,
    p.full_name,
    COUNT(pt.pet_id) as pet_count,
    GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT pt.species) as species_owned
FROM credit_cards cc 
JOIN medical_records mr ON cc.owner_id = mr.owner_id 
JOIN people p ON p.person_id = cc.owner_id

input.query:

    cc.owner_id,
    p.full_name,
    COUNT(pt.pet_id) as pet_count,
    GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT pt.species) as species_owned
FROM credit_cards cc 
JOIN medical_records mr ON cc.owner_id = mr.owner_id 
JOIN people p ON p.person_id = cc.owner_id 
LEFT JOIN pets pt ON pt.owner_id = cc.owner_id
WHERE mr.blood_type = 'O-' AND cc.provider = 'American Express'
GROUP BY cc.owner_id, p.full_name
ORDER BY pet_count DESC
